notes: Grind size too high. Try 6-7 next time. Very sour
Getting better. More bitter than sour. Increase grind size and see what happens next
Waited 10sec between lock and push. Not bitter nor sour!
Grind too coarse, easy to push pressure. Increase grind
Opps. Made it coarser instead of more fine. Came out fast
Messed up by grinding it to fine. Try 13 next. Bitter, but getting better
Better. Still a bit better, but getting there. Lets try 14.5 next for grind size
Probably one of the smoothest coffee's I've had so far. Slightly bitter, but getting better. Lets try 14, and really put that pressure down next
A bit sour. Let's do 14.5 next. For pressure, lately (including this one), I'm going off feel (probably somewhere between 6-8)
Bitter. Look at notes from last session because that was pretty good and go from there
Too sour. Went through too fast. Try 14 next. Without putting any pressure, I was getting 4 bars. Too coarse
